{"tid":2055182,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"連登PR 最新推post玩法","createTime":"2020-06-07T18:05:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-08T00:50:16.000Z","uid":102255,"like":21,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"54a6c882951c909ff7caebf63ff32661d1cc2c04","tid":2055182,"uid":102255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T18:05:27.000Z","msg":"前排出完個post 引咗成班PR帶風向狗上水，自從個次點晒名之後就觀察咗幾個禮拜，以前個group 人淨係帶死一個風向，好易反艇，依家進化咗嘅玩法，不妨參考下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家鬥黃嘅post 多咗，不外乎針對所謂假黃/人血饅頭，班PR 狗入到去都係採取一個good cop bad cop 嘅策略，一個狂踩一個就狂讚。當然本身呢個策略本身係令個受盤問嘅人和盤托出，但喺討論區入面就可以將個討論spin 到好兩極化，特別係用再將個討論推向極端嘅例子，e.g. 明明講緊幅壁畫，佢話印落張銀紙到好唔撚好<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家香港咁亂，無論網上戰線/香城online 啲post都係雷聲大雨點少，另外一大班97前就聚焦晒係英國，成個熱門最撚多人推就係啲鬥黃post<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依個平台就嚟玩撚完架啦，希望手足們多善用twitter, 中文好英文好，最緊要與世界接軌，兒登就留返班傻撚係到圍爐劣鳩，最重要提醒埋身邊嘅人，好多懵撚cdrom 睇乜就信<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46547aad18cb87f71111fce3d081d4371826cd8f","tid":2055182,"uid":8482,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T18:05:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"13427bcae23316969616a8103d8e6bcaeabf871d","tid":2055182,"uid":8482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T18:06:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2d7da685e47f153fae36380ab4da6afe203272b6","tid":2055182,"uid":70487,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T18:06:47.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"color: maroon;\">[&darr;&darr;港獨強心針&darr;&darr;]<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">香港最強力盟友USA : <br />\n國際反共 形勢大好<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/pAcopPX\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/pAcopPX</a></span></span></div>"},{"pid":"b37837505fd307d94fe08fab0ac79b7f8fcabe2a","tid":2055182,"uid":33874,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T18:10:20.000Z","msg":"英國批移民<br />\n97前和理非/勇武走哂<br />\n97後勇武拉哂<br />\n仲有香城online?"},{"pid":"e459d365b88d9d3fcab2897ad52a9bdba65fa716","tid":2055182,"uid":162268,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T18:19:01.000Z","msg":"真係明明講緊幅壁畫<br />\n點知就spin咗去人血饅頭到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9da4d75329fac30513123c1fa1213bec0b0fccf7","tid":2055182,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T20:03:22.000Z","msg":"推 推 推 ！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7ee9385bb1f9fee74e94b7341210adccbecabce","tid":2055182,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T20:06:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c063392bbc00291fddfd8df8d3e57fc7208a211","tid":2055182,"uid":24596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T22:03:59.000Z","msg":"當然唔止係咁<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2014324/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2014324/page/1</a><br />\n我又唔知你點應對呢到時？"},{"pid":"b9b38a04f2a000b656804df841c3dab9d35a3892","tid":2055182,"uid":24596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T22:14:43.000Z","msg":"係呀block咗我呀嗎，我覆咗你認為係pr post個post呀嗎，我係pr呀嗎<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2014286/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2014286/page/1</a><br />\n我誠心向你道歉好唔好？"},{"pid":"61404ef33a7a4cbdc74495c03a9869aaadb8dab6","tid":2055182,"uid":24596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T22:29:28.000Z","msg":"本來以為有咩咁巴閉，擇曬人名，原來淨係得觀察<br />\n你係要當連登係資訊中轉站而唔係討論區嘅，你何必介意人地講乜？<br />\n你係咪應該出post呼籲連登只係資訊中轉站，唔好回應？<br />\n你係咪應該搵志同道合嘅一齊洗地呀？連登唔係有洗地組？<br />\n根據我觀察，只要三個人，半個鐘，不斷推post一定上到熱門<br />\n一係一組18人將一個鐘每5分鐘分成12小段，每人每小時按自己分段推<br />\n請問做咗未？<br />\n你係咪應該將5毛名單post長期置頂？<br />\n你係咪應該立個區規等志同道合嘅一齊守一齊玩？"},{"pid":"a106e3e7d276e696c8fdeb16791bd053e3942b7b","tid":2055182,"uid":24596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T22:30:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1653178/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1653178/page/1</a><br />\n一係幫手update?"},{"pid":"4e328eca274712df3cae13ec29259cc9aa547d33","tid":2055182,"uid":24596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T22:33:06.000Z","msg":"等咗咁耐睇下有咩料到<br />\n又擇曬名又盛<br />\n結果出個咁嘅post<br />\n其實半年前已經有人講過喇最新玩法"},{"pid":"444af199729a35a04aca54a1f162f50ae4875746","tid":2055182,"uid":24596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T22:36:03.000Z","msg":"哇5點鐘係咁推post，仲唔係pr5毛"},{"pid":"2fce2f775845ca966a4028d7792383e8e7a2bd3d","tid":2055182,"uid":162954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T22:40:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/